# USAF Joint Logistics Drone Fleet Coordination Algorithm  
**Contract:** FA8802-25-D-0034 | **Classification:** SECRET | **Phase:** IOC Preparation  
**Scope:** Technical specification for fleet coordination algorithm supporting 48-logistics drone fleet at 3 FOBs in CENTCOM AOR. Focus: optimal routing, weather integration, battery management, ADS-B deconfliction, failure recovery.  

---

## 1. Core Algorithm: Constrained Multi-Objective Path Planner (CMOPP)  
*Replaces legacy greedy nearest-neighbor with dynamic programming-based solver respecting all constraints.*  

### 1.1 Input Data Model  
```json
{
  "fleet_state": [
    {
      "drone_id": "string (UUID)",
      "current_location": {"lat": float, "lon": float, "alt": float},
      "soc": float (0.0-1.0), // State-of-Charge
      "payload": {
        "type": "enum [MEDICAL, AMMO, MRE]",
        "weight_kg": float,
        "priority": "int (1-3, 3=highest)" // Medical=3, Ammo=2, MRE=1
      },
      "max_range_km": float, // Derived from SOC + payload
      "reserve_threshold": float (0.20), // 20% SOC reserve mandatory
      "status": "enum [IDLE, EN_ROUTE, LOADING, UNLOADING, EMERGENCY]"
    }
  ],
  "delivery_points": [
    {
      "foB_id": "string",
      "location": {"lat": float, "lon": float, "alt": float},
      "demand": {
        "MEDICAL": int,
        "AMMO": int,
        "MRE": int
      },
      "time_window": {
        "earliest": "ISO 8601 timestamp",
        "latest": "ISO 8601 timestamp"
      },
      "priority": "int (1-5)" // Higher = critical resupply
    }
  ],
  "weather_forecast": { // Updated every 15 min from NOAA via SIPRNET
    "metar": { "station_id": string, "obs_time": string, "wind": {...}, "visibility": float, "ceiling": float, ... },
    "taf": { "station_id": string, "valid_from": string, "valid_to": string, "forecast": [...] }
  },
  "ads_b_traffic": [ // Real-time from Link 16/ADSB-IN
    {
      "icao": string,
      "position": {"lat": float, "lon": float, "alt": float},
      "velocity": {"gs": float, "track": float, "vs": float},
      "emergency_status": boolean,
      "flight_plan": { "origin": string, "destination": string, "eta": string }
    }
  ],
  "no_fly_zones": [ // Static + dynamic (e.g., pop-up threats)
    {
      "id": string,
      "geometry": { "type": "Polygon", "coordinates": [[[float, float]]] },
      "active_from": "ISO 8601",
      "active_to": "ISO 8601",
      "reason": "string"
    }
  ]
}
```

